{
  "stem": "13911.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there, as far as I was, you know, a young girl, for me-- first of all, it was very exciting when the Russians came in with the tanks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, everybody-- and all the kids ran too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was so-- but when do you see tanks rolling on your little streets, you know, and the Russians waving?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was euphoria.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So to me, it was-- ah, it was so exciting, terrific.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the Russians came, of course, and introduced their system, which means liquidating every private business, which my father's business was taken away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no such a thing like you're a proprietor of something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we had-- in that committee that was-- how do you-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Confiscating-- was a friend of ours-- and he gave us notice that, let's say, Thursday, they're going to confiscate my father's business.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we would make a few trips and salvage a little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were boxes of powder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were perfumed soap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, in those days, most people didn't use fancy aromatic soap.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, whatever is-- it was good enough that they washed, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we had soaps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was like a-- a jewel, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we, whatever we could, we brought home, which later on came in very handy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When we were in the ghetto and had nothing else to eat, the Pole would sneak up to the fence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We would give him a bar of soap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He would give us two potatoes or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that came in so handy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So your father was able to salvage many things, or--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, a little.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just took out whatever, figuring maybe-- not that we needed the powder to powder ourselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But maybe it will be-- you need it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
